SocioMeet , is a metting support application for only personal use.

It provides various functionalities like
1.  Set the meeting venue using google maps
2.  Let users accept and reject the invitations by sending sms to an inbound number
3.  A simple application if installed on a GPS enabled phone , wil also let the user keep notified about where on the globe is the person and how much time will it take for him to reach the venue of a meeting that he was invited to
4.  Get directions for users from  their current point to the venue through sms

Innovation
1.  Using GPS location and informing the invitees on the right time acout the meeting and the directions being sent to their phones
2.  A desktop client which can be used on any operating system

